name: Twin |-
description:
When we see twins alone is hard to identify who is who but easy to see the subtle differences if they're together.
These both pieces were conceived at the same time in two different computers to experiment how the development of one can alter or help the creation of the other.
Both are the same, but both are different.

As Twins are.

This piece (Twin |-) will be sent to first owners of the other one (Twin -|)
